SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

SELECT 
    [Limit1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
    [Limit1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Limit1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
    [Limit1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
    [Limit1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
    [Limit1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
    [Limit1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
    [Limit1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
    [Limit1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
    [Limit1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
        [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Extent1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
        [Extent1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
        [Extent1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
        [Extent1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
        [Extent1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
        [Extent1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
        [Extent1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
        [Extent1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
        [Extent1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
        FROM  [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvr_user_id]
        WHERE (1 = [Extent2].[uvr_role_id]) AND ([Extent1].[user_name] = @p__linq__0) AND (([Extent1].[user_password] = @p__linq__1) OR (([Extent1].[user_password] IS NULL) AND (@p__linq__1 IS NULL)))
    )  AS [Limit1]

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

    )  AS [GroupBy1]

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

SELECT 
    [Limit1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
    [Limit1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Limit1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
    [Limit1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
    [Limit1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
    [Limit1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
    [Limit1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
    [Limit1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
    [Limit1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
    [Limit1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
        [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Extent1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
        [Extent1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
        [Extent1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
        [Extent1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
        [Extent1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
        [Extent1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
        [Extent1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
        [Extent1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
        [Extent1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
        FROM  [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[User_vs_Role] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[user_id] = [Extent2].[uvr_user_id]
        WHERE ([Extent1].[user_name] = @p__linq__0) AND (([Extent1].[user_password] = @p__linq__1) OR (([Extent1].[user_password] IS NULL) AND (@p__linq__1 IS NULL)))
    )  AS [Limit1]

    [Limit1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name],

    [Limit1].[stu_photo_path] AS [stu_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
    [Limit1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex], 
    [Limit1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Limit1].[C2] AS [C2]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[stu_id] AS [stu_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name], 
        [Extent1].[stu_card_type] AS [stu_card_type], 
        [Extent1].[stu_idCard] AS [stu_idCard], 
        [Extent1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex], 
        [Extent1].[stu_birthday] AS [stu_birthday], 
        [Extent1].[stu_photo_path] AS [stu_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[stu_phone] AS [stu_phone], 
        [Extent1].[stu_email] AS [stu_email], 
        [Extent1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] AS [stu_grade_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_home_address] AS [stu_home_address], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[school_name] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[grade_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[grade_name] END AS [C2]
        FROM   [dbo].[Student_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_School] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[stu_school_id] = [Extent2].[school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Grade] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] = [Extent3].[grade_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Limit1]

    FROM ( SELECT

        [Extent1].[svc_add_time] AS [svc_add_time], 
        [Extent2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Extent2].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
        [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Extent4].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
        @p__linq__1 AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[svc_is_end] = 1) THEN N'完结' ELSE N'进行中' END AS [C2]
        FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svc_course_id] = [Extent2].[course_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent2].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[svc_stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[svc_add_time] ASC

    [Limit1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex],

    [Limit1].[C2] AS [C2]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[stu_id] AS [stu_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name], 
        [Extent1].[stu_card_type] AS [stu_card_type], 
        [Extent1].[stu_idCard] AS [stu_idCard], 
        [Extent1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex],

        [Extent1].[stu_phone] AS [stu_phone], 
        [Extent1].[stu_email] AS [stu_email], 
        [Extent1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] AS [stu_grade_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_home_address] AS [stu_home_address], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[school_name] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[grade_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[grade_name] END AS [C2]
        FROM   [dbo].[Student_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_School] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[stu_school_id] = [Extent2].[school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Grade] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] = [Extent3].[grade_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Limit1]

    [Project1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
    [Project1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
        [Extent1].[svc_add_time] AS [svc_add_time], 
        [Extent2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Extent2].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
        [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Extent4].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
        @p__linq__1 AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[svc_is_end] = 1) THEN N'完结' ELSE N'进行中' END AS [C2]
        FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svc_course_id] = [Extent2].[course_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent2].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[svc_stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[svc_add_time] ASC

SELECT 
    [Project1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
    [Project1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
        [Extent1].[svc_add_time] AS [svc_add_time], 
        [Extent2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Extent2].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
        [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Extent4].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
        @p__linq__1 AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[svc_is_end] = 1) THEN N'完结' ELSE N'进行中' END AS [C2]
        FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svc_course_id] = [Extent2].[course_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent2].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[svc_stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[svc_add_time] ASC

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[MigrationId] DESC

    [Limit1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name],

    [Limit1].[stu_photo_path] AS [stu_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
    [Limit1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex], 
    [Limit1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Limit1].[C2] AS [C2]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[stu_id] AS [stu_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name], 
        [Extent1].[stu_card_type] AS [stu_card_type], 
        [Extent1].[stu_idCard] AS [stu_idCard], 
        [Extent1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex], 
        [Extent1].[stu_birthday] AS [stu_birthday], 
        [Extent1].[stu_photo_path] AS [stu_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[stu_phone] AS [stu_phone], 
        [Extent1].[stu_email] AS [stu_email], 
        [Extent1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] AS [stu_grade_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_home_address] AS [stu_home_address], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[school_name] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[grade_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[grade_name] END AS [C2]
        FROM   [dbo].[Student_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_School] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[stu_school_id] = [Extent2].[school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Grade] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] = [Extent3].[grade_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Limit1]

    [Limit1].[stu_home_address] AS [stu_home_address], 
    [Limit1].[stu_birthday] AS [stu_birthday], 
    [Limit1].[stu_email] AS [stu_email], 
    [Limit1].[stu_grade_id] AS [stu_grade_id], 
    [Limit1].[stu_id] AS [stu_id], 
    [Limit1].[stu_idCard] AS [stu_idCard], 
    [Limit1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name], 
    [Limit1].[stu_phone] AS [stu_phone], 
    [Limit1].[stu_photo_path] AS [stu_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
    [Limit1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex], 
    [Limit1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Limit1].[C2] AS [C2]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[stu_id] AS [stu_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_name] AS [stu_name], 
        [Extent1].[stu_card_type] AS [stu_card_type], 
        [Extent1].[stu_idCard] AS [stu_idCard], 
        [Extent1].[stu_sex] AS [stu_sex], 
        [Extent1].[stu_birthday] AS [stu_birthday], 
        [Extent1].[stu_photo_path] AS [stu_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[stu_phone] AS [stu_phone], 
        [Extent1].[stu_email] AS [stu_email], 
        [Extent1].[stu_school_id] AS [stu_school_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] AS [stu_grade_id], 
        [Extent1].[stu_home_address] AS [stu_home_address], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent2].[school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent2].[school_name] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent3].[grade_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Extent3].[grade_name] END AS [C2]
        FROM   [dbo].[Student_Info] AS [Extent1]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_School] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[stu_school_id] = [Extent2].[school_id]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Grade] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[stu_grade_id] = [Extent3].[grade_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Limit1]
-- p__linq__0: '2017100001' (Type = String, Size = 4000)
-- Executing at 2017/10/27 11:38:47 +08:00
-- Completed in 0 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
    [Project1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
        [Extent1].[svc_add_time] AS [svc_add_time], 
        [Extent2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Extent2].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
        [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Extent4].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
        @p__linq__1 AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[svc_is_end] = 1) THEN N'完结' ELSE N'进行中' END AS [C2]
        FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svc_course_id] = [Extent2].[course_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent2].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[svc_stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[svc_add_time] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '2017100001' (Type = String, Size = 4000)
-- p__linq__1: '2017100001' (Type = String, Size = 4000)
-- Executing at 2017/10/27 11:38:47 +08:00
-- Completed in 0 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Limit1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
    [Limit1].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
    [Limit1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Limit1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Limit1].[svc_pay] AS [svc_pay], 
    [Limit1].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
    [Limit1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Limit1].[C2] AS [C2], 
    [Limit1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
    [Limit1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[svc_course_id] AS [svc_course_id], 
        [Extent1].[svc_pay] AS [svc_pay], 
        [Extent2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Extent2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Extent2].[course_cost] AS [course_cost], 
        [Extent2].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
        [Extent3].[c_season_name] AS [c_season_name], 
        [Extent4].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[svc_is_end] = 1) THEN N'完结' ELSE N'进行中' END AS [C1], 
        @p__linq__2 AS [C2]
        FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svc_course_id] = [Extent2].[course_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[c_cs_id] = [Extent3].[c_season_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent2].[c_sub_id] = [Extent4].[sub_id]
        WHERE ([Extent1].[svc_stu_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent1].[svc_course_id] = @p__linq__1)
    )  AS [Limit1]

SELECT 
    [Extent1].[svct_cvt_id] AS [svct_cvt_id], 
     CAST( [Extent2].[cvt_time] AS nvarchar(max)) AS [C1], 
    [Extent1].[svct_roll_call] AS [svct_roll_call], 
    [Extent4].[rc_name] AS [rc_name]
    FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_CTimes] AS [Extent1]
    INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_vs_Time] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svct_cvt_id] = [Extent2].[cvt_id]
    INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[cvt_course_id] = [Extent3].[course_id]
    INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Roll_Call] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[svct_roll_call] = [Extent4].[rc_id]
    WHERE ([Extent1].[svct_stu_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent3].[course_id] = @p__linq__1)

        CASE WHEN ([Extent1].[svc_is_end] = 1) THEN N'完结' ELSE N'进行中' END AS [C2]
        FROM    [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent1]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[svc_course_id] = [Extent2].[course_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent2].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
        INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent2].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
        WHERE [Extent1].[svc_stu_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[svc_add_time] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '2017100001' (Type = String, Size = 4000)
-- p__linq__1: '2017100001' (Type = String, Size = 4000)

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model],

    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion],

        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1],

    [Limit1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
    [Limit1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Limit1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
    [Limit1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
    [Limit1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
    [Limit1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
    [Limit1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
    [Limit1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
    [Limit1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address],

    [Limit1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_time] AS [user_update_time], 
    [Limit1].[user_update_user] AS [user_update_user], 
    [Limit1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]
    FROM ( SELECT TOP (1) 
        [Extent1].[user_id] AS [user_id], 
        [Extent1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Extent1].[user_photo_path] AS [user_photo_path], 
        [Extent1].[user_phone] AS [user_phone], 
        [Extent1].[user_info] AS [user_info], 
        [Extent1].[user_email] AS [user_email], 
        [Extent1].[user_password] AS [user_password], 
        [Extent1].[user_Occupation] AS [user_Occupation], 
        [Extent1].[user_home_address] AS [user_home_address], 
        [Extent1].[user_work_unit] AS [user_work_unit], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_time] AS [user_add_time], 
        [Extent1].[user_add_user] AS [user_add_user],

        [Extent1].[user_login_times] AS [user_login_times]

    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
    [Project3].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
        [Project2].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C1]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId],

SELECT TOP (1) 
    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion], 
        1 AS [C1]
        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT

                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info],

        )  AS [Project2]

    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used],

                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]

                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id],

                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]

                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info],

                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]

                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '4' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)

                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT

                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id],

            FROM ( SELECT

                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info],

    [Project1].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
    [Project1].[Model] AS [Model], 
    [Project1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[MigrationId] AS [MigrationId], 
        [Extent1].[Model] AS [Model], 
        [Extent1].[ProductVersion] AS [ProductVersion],

        FROM [dbo].[__MigrationHistory] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[ContextKey] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]

        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

            FROM ( SELECT

                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id],

        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '4' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'True' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

-- Completed in 0 ms with result: SqlDataReader

        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE ([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]

            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '4' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

-- Completed in 12 ms with result: SqlDataReader

    [Project1].[log_time] AS [log_time],

    FROM ( SELECT

        [Extent1].[log_user_ip] AS [log_user_ip], 
        [Extent1].[log_time] AS [log_time], 
        [Extent1].[log_device] AS [log_device],

        FROM [dbo].[Sys_Log] AS [Extent1]

    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[log_time] ASC

Closed connection at 2017/11/3 16:37:44 +08:00
Opened connection at 2017/11/3 16:37:44 +08:00
SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '4' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

-- Completed in 13 ms with result: SqlDataReader

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC
-- p__linq__0: '4' (Type = Int32, IsNullable = false)
-- p__linq__1: 'False' (Type = Boolean, IsNullable = false)

SELECT 
    [Project3].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
    [Project3].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
    [Project3].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
    [Project3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
    [Project3].[C1] AS [C1], 
    [Project3].[C4] AS [C2], 
    [Project3].[C2] AS [C3], 
    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project3].[C3] AS [C4]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Project2].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
        [Project2].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
        [Project2].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
        [Project2].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
        [Project2].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
        [Project2].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[c_time_info] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[c_time_info] END AS [C1], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[room_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[room_name] END AS [C2], 
        CASE WHEN ([Project2].[sys_school_name] IS NULL) THEN N'' ELSE [Project2].[sys_school_name] END AS [C3], 
        [Project2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
        [Project2].[C1] AS [C4]
        FROM ( SELECT 
            [Project1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
            [Project1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
            [Project1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
            [Project1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
            [Project1].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
            [Project1].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
            [Project1].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
            [Project1].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
            [Project1].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
            [Project1].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name], 
            (SELECT 
                COUNT(1) AS [A1]
                FROM [dbo].[Student_vs_Course] AS [Extent7]
                WHERE [Extent7].[svc_course_id] = [Project1].[course_id]) AS [C1]
            FROM ( SELECT 
                [Extent1].[course_id] AS [course_id], 
                [Extent1].[course_name] AS [course_name], 
                [Extent1].[c_sub_id] AS [c_sub_id], 
                [Extent1].[c_time_info] AS [c_time_info], 
                [Extent3].[sub_name] AS [sub_name], 
                [Extent4].[c_season_id] AS [c_season_id], 
                [Extent4].[c_is_used] AS [c_is_used], 
                [Extent2].[user_name] AS [user_name], 
                [Extent5].[room_name] AS [room_name], 
                [Extent6].[sys_school_name] AS [sys_school_name]
                FROM      [dbo].[Course_Info] AS [Extent1]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[User_Info] AS [Extent2] ON [Extent1].[c_assistant_id] = [Extent2].[user_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Dic_Subject] AS [Extent3] ON [Extent1].[c_sub_id] = [Extent3].[sub_id]
                INNER JOIN [dbo].[Course_Season] AS [Extent4] ON [Extent1].[c_cs_id] = [Extent4].[c_season_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_ClassRoom] AS [Extent5] ON [Extent1].[c_room] = [Extent5].[room_id]
                LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[Sys_School] AS [Extent6] ON [Extent5].[room_school_id] = [Extent6].[sys_school_id]
                WHERE (CASE WHEN (([Extent1].[c_teacher_id] = @p__linq__0) AND ([Extent4].[c_is_used] = @p__linq__1)) THEN [Extent4].[c_is_used] ELSE cast(1 as bit) END) = 1
            )  AS [Project1]
        )  AS [Project2]
    )  AS [Project3]
    ORDER BY [Project3].[c_is_used] ASC, [Project3].[c_season_id] ASC, [Project3].[c_sub_id] ASC

    [Project1].[log_device] AS [log_device], 
    [Project1].[log_info] AS [log_info]
    FROM ( SELECT 
        [Extent1].[log_user_id] AS [log_user_id], 
        [Extent1].[log_user_ip] AS [log_user_ip], 
        [Extent1].[log_time] AS [log_time], 
        [Extent1].[log_device] AS [log_device], 
        [Extent1].[log_info] AS [log_info]
        FROM [dbo].[Sys_Log] AS [Extent1]
        WHERE [Extent1].[log_user_id] = @p__linq__0
    )  AS [Project1]
    ORDER BY [Project1].[log_time] ASC
